  <brief_title>Use of a Pressurized Face Mask for Preventing Respiratory Complications After Chest Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4, Randomized, Controlled Trial on the Efficacy as Prophylaxis of Postoperative Respiratory Complications and Safety of Continuous Positive Airways Pressure (CPAP) Applied Throughout Boussignac Mask During the Immediate Postoperative Period of Patients Undergoing Lung Resection</official_title>
